Package lexrParsr.RecPy

Interface RecPyParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
RecPyParserBaseListener
public interface RecPyParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by RecPyParser.
